  <entry>
    <title>OpenVAS 社区版问题排查与解决指南</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/04/OpenVAS-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%E7%89%88%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/04/OpenVAS-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%E7%89%88%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="OpenVAS-社区版问题排查与解决指南"><a href="#OpenVAS-社区版问题排查与解决指南" class="headerlink" title="OpenVAS 社区版问题排查与解决指南"></a>OpenVAS 社区版问题排查与解决指南</h1><h2 id="环境信息"><a href="#环境信息" class="headerlink" title="环境信息"></a>环境信息</h2><ul><li><strong>系统</strong>: Linux (Docker)</li><li><strong>OpenVAS 版本</strong>: Greenbone Community Edition 24.x</li><li><strong>部署方式</strong>: Docker Compose</li></ul><hr><h2 id="问题一：Web-UI-显示-404"><a href="#问题一：Web-UI-显示-404" class="headerlink" title="问题一：Web UI 显示 404"></a>问题一：Web UI 显示 404</h2><h3 id="现象"><a href="#现象" class="headerlink" title="现象"></a>现象</h3><p>访问 <code>http://IP:9392/</code> 返回 404 错误</p><h3 id="原因分析"><a href="#原因分析" class="headerlink" title="原因分析"></a>原因分析</h3><p>gsad 容器启动参数是 <code>--http-only --api-only -f</code>，这是 <strong>API-only 模式</strong>，不提供 Web UI 静态页面，只提供 GMP API 接口。</p><h3 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h3><p>需要添加 gsa 容器来生成静态文件，然后用 nginx 提供 Web UI。</p><ol><li><strong>添加 gsa 容器</strong>（生成静态文件）:</li></ol><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">gsa:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">image:</span> <span class="hljs-string">registry.community.greenbone.net/community/gsa:stable-slim</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">environment:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">MOUNT_PATH:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/mnt/web&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">KEEP_ALIVE:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">healthcheck:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">test:</span> [<span class="hljs-string">&quot;CMD-SHELL&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;test -e /run/gsa/copying.done&quot;</span>]<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">start_period:</span> <span class="hljs-string">5s</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">gsa_data_vol:/mnt/web</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li><strong>添加 nginx 容器</strong>（提供 Web 服务）:</li></ol><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">nginx:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">image:</span> <span class="hljs-string">nginx</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">container_name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">openvas-nginx</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">environment:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">NGINX_HOST:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">NGINX_HTTP_PORT:</span> <span class="hljs-number">9392</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">ports:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-number">9392</span><span class="hljs-string">:9392</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">gsa_data_vol:/usr/share/nginx/html:ro</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">depends_on:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">gsa:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">condition:</span> <span class="hljs-string">service_healthy</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">gsad:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">condition:</span> <span class="hljs-string">service_started</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">command:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-string">sh</span> <span class="hljs-string">-c</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;echo &#x27;upstream gsad &#123; server gsad:9392; &#125; server &#123; client_max_body_size 1000m; listen 9392; location ~ ^/(gmp|system_report|logout) &#123; proxy_pass http://gsad; proxy_set_header Host $$host; proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $$remote_addr; &#125; location / &#123; root /usr/share/nginx/html; index index.html; try_files $$uri $$uri/ /index.html; &#125; &#125;&#x27; &gt; /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf &amp;&amp; nginx -g &#x27;daemon off;&#x27;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="问题二：无法创建扫描任务（扫描配置不可用）"><a href="#问题二：无法创建扫描任务（扫描配置不可用）" class="headerlink" title="问题二：无法创建扫描任务（扫描配置不可用）"></a>问题二：无法创建扫描任务（扫描配置不可用）</h2><h3 id="现象-1"><a href="#现象-1" class="headerlink" title="现象"></a>现象</h3><p>Web UI 可以登录，但创建扫描任务时提示”扫描配置不可用”或配置下拉菜单为空</p><h3 id="诊断步骤"><a href="#诊断步骤" class="headerlink" title="诊断步骤"></a>诊断步骤</h3><ol><li><strong>检查 configs 表</strong>:</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-pg-gvm-1 psql -U gvmd -d gvmd -c <span class="hljs-string">&quot;SELECT name FROM configs;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果返回 0 行，说明扫描配置没有加载。</p><ol start="2"><li><strong>检查 NVT 数据</strong>:</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-pg-gvm-1 psql -U gvmd -d gvmd -c <span class="hljs-string">&quot;SELECT count(*) FROM nvts;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果返回 0，说明 VT（漏洞测试脚本）没有同步到数据库。</p><ol start="3"><li><strong>检查 gvmd 日志</strong>:</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker logs openvas-community-gvmd-1 2&gt;&amp;1 | <span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -50<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关键日志信息：</p><ul><li><code>No SCAP database found</code> - SCAP 数据库未初始化</li><li><code>OSP service has different VT status</code> - VT 数据需要同步</li><li><code>Failed to open lock file</code> - 权限问题</li></ul><h3 id="常见原因及解决方案"><a href="#常见原因及解决方案" class="headerlink" title="常见原因及解决方案"></a>常见原因及解决方案</h3><h4 id="原因-A：SCAP-数据库未同步"><a href="#原因-A：SCAP-数据库未同步" class="headerlink" title="原因 A：SCAP 数据库未同步"></a>原因 A：SCAP 数据库未同步</h4><p><strong>症状</strong>: 日志显示 <code>No SCAP database found</code> 或 <code>rebuilding SCAP db from scratch</code></p><p><strong>解决</strong>: 等待 SCAP 数据同步完成（约 30-60 分钟）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 监控同步进度</span><br>docker logs openvas-community-gvmd-1 2&gt;&amp;1 | grep -E <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Updating|Done|succeeded&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同步完成标志：</p><ul><li><code>Updating SCAP info succeeded</code></li><li><code>Updating CVSS scores and CVE counts for CPEs</code> 完成</li></ul><h4 id="原因-B：VT-同步卡住"><a href="#原因-B：VT-同步卡住" class="headerlink" title="原因 B：VT 同步卡住"></a>原因 B：VT 同步卡住</h4><p><strong>症状</strong>: 日志停在 <code>Updating VTs from scanner</code>，但 nvts 表仍为 0</p><p><strong>解决步骤</strong>:</p><ol><li>检查 feed 锁文件：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-gvmd-1 <span class="hljs-built_in">ls</span> -la /var/lib/gvm/feed-update.lock<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>如果锁文件存在但进程卡住，删除锁文件并重启：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-gvmd-1 <span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -f /var/lib/gvm/feed-update.lock<br>docker restart openvas-community-gvmd-1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>检查 ospd-openvas 状态：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker logs openvas-community-ospd-openvas-1 2&gt;&amp;1 | <span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -20<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="原因-C：权限问题"><a href="#原因-C：权限问题" class="headerlink" title="原因 C：权限问题"></a>原因 C：权限问题</h4><p><strong>症状</strong>: 日志显示 <code>Failed to open lock file: Permission denied</code></p><p><strong>解决</strong>:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 修复 /var/lib/gvm 目录权限</span><br>docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-gvmd-1 <span class="hljs-built_in">chown</span> -R gvmd:gvmd /var/lib/gvm/<br>docker restart openvas-community-gvmd-1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="原因-D：PostgreSQL-锁文件冲突"><a href="#原因-D：PostgreSQL-锁文件冲突" class="headerlink" title="原因 D：PostgreSQL 锁文件冲突"></a>原因 D：PostgreSQL 锁文件冲突</h4><p><strong>症状</strong>: pg-gvm 容器不断重启，日志显示 <code>lock file already exists</code></p><p><strong>解决</strong>:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 删除 PostgreSQL socket 锁文件</span><br>docker run --<span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -v openvas-community_psql_socket_vol:/data alpine <span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -f /data/.s.PGSQL.5432.lock<br>docker restart openvas-community-pg-gvm-1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="问题三：容器健康检查失败"><a href="#问题三：容器健康检查失败" class="headerlink" title="问题三：容器健康检查失败"></a>问题三：容器健康检查失败</h2><h3 id="现象-2"><a href="#现象-2" class="headerlink" title="现象"></a>现象</h3><p>某些容器（如 data-objects、scap-data）显示 unhealthy</p><h3 id="诊断"><a href="#诊断" class="headerlink" title="诊断"></a>诊断</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker ps -a | grep -E <span class="hljs-string">&quot;unhealthy|Restarting&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="解决"><a href="#解决" class="headerlink" title="解决"></a>解决</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看具体容器的健康检查日志</span><br>docker inspect --format=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#123;&#123;json .State.Health&#125;&#125;&#x27;</span> openvas-community-data-objects-1 | jq<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 重启不健康的容器</span><br>docker restart openvas-community-data-objects-1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="问题四：信号量权限错误"><a href="#问题四：信号量权限错误" class="headerlink" title="问题四：信号量权限错误"></a>问题四：信号量权限错误</h2><h3 id="现象-3"><a href="#现象-3" class="headerlink" title="现象"></a>现象</h3><p>执行 gvmd 命令时出现：</p><figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nix"><span class="hljs-params">init_semaphore_set:</span> error getting semaphore set <span class="hljs-params">info:</span> Permission denied<br><span class="hljs-params">semaphore_op:</span> semaphore operation <span class="hljs-params">failed:</span> Permission denied<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="原因"><a href="#原因" class="headerlink" title="原因"></a>原因</h3><p>gvmd 容器以 root 运行，但 gvmd 守护进程以 gvmd 用户运行，命令行工具与守护进程竞争信号量。</p><h3 id="解决方案-1"><a href="#解决方案-1" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h3><p><strong>方案 1</strong>: 以 gvmd 用户身份执行命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> -u gvmd openvas-community-gvmd-1 gvmd --get-scanners<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>方案 2</strong>: 通过运行中的守护进程执行（不推荐直接运行 gvmd 命令）</p><hr><h2 id="完整的状态检查清单"><a href="#完整的状态检查清单" class="headerlink" title="完整的状态检查清单"></a>完整的状态检查清单</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-meta">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># OpenVAS 状态检查脚本</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== 容器状态 ===&quot;</span><br>docker ps -a | grep -E <span class="hljs-string">&quot;gvmd|gsad|nginx|pg-gvm|ospd|openvasd&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== 数据库连接 ===&quot;</span><br>docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-pg-gvm-1 psql -U gvmd -d gvmd -c <span class="hljs-string">&quot;SELECT &#x27;connected&#x27; as status;&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== 扫描配置 ===&quot;</span><br>docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-pg-gvm-1 psql -U gvmd -d gvmd -c <span class="hljs-string">&quot;SELECT name FROM configs;&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== NVT 数量 ===&quot;</span><br>docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-pg-gvm-1 psql -U gvmd -d gvmd -c <span class="hljs-string">&quot;SELECT count(*) as nvt_count FROM nvts;&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== Feed 锁状态 ===&quot;</span><br>docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> openvas-community-gvmd-1 <span class="hljs-built_in">ls</span> -la /var/lib/gvm/feed-update.lock 2&gt;&amp;1 || <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;无锁文件&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== gvmd 最新日志 ===&quot;</span><br>docker logs openvas-community-gvmd-1 2&gt;&amp;1 | <span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -10<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== ospd-openvas 最新日志 ===&quot;</span><br>docker logs openvas-community-ospd-openvas-1 2&gt;&amp;1 | <span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -5<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=== Web UI 测试 ===&quot;</span><br>curl -sI http://localhost:9392/ | <span class="hljs-built_in">head</span> -3<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="关键日志关键词"><a href="#关键日志关键词" class="headerlink" title="关键日志关键词"></a>关键日志关键词</h2><table><thead><tr><th>关键词</th><th>含义</th><th>处理建议</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>No SCAP database found</code></td><td>SCAP 数据库未初始化</td><td>等待自动同步</td></tr><tr><td><code>rebuilding SCAP db from scratch</code></td><td>正在重建 SCAP 数据库</td><td>等待完成</td></tr><tr><td><code>Updating SCAP info succeeded</code></td><td>SCAP 同步完成</td><td>✅ 正常</td></tr><tr><td><code>OSP service has different VT status</code></td><td>VT 需要同步</td><td>等待或手动触发</td></tr><tr><td><code>Failed to open lock file</code></td><td>权限问题</td><td>修复目录权限</td></tr><tr><td><code>lock file already exists</code></td><td>锁冲突</td><td>删除锁文件重启</td></tr><tr><td><code>configs has been created</code></td><td>配置已加载</td><td>✅ 正常</td></tr><tr><td><code>Finished loading VTs</code></td><td>VT 加载完成</td><td>✅ 正常</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="预防措施"><a href="#预防措施" class="headerlink" title="预防措施"></a>预防措施</h2><ol><li><p><strong>首次部署后耐心等待</strong></p><ul><li>SCAP 数据同步需要 30-60 分钟</li><li>VT 同步需要 5-10 分钟</li><li>不要频繁重启容器</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>定期检查日志</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 添加到定时任务</span><br>0 */6 * * * docker logs openvas-community-gvmd-1 2&gt;&amp;1 | <span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -20<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>数据卷备份</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 备份 PostgreSQL 数据</span><br>docker run --<span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -v openvas-community_psql_data_vol:/data -v $(<span class="hljs-built_in">pwd</span>):/backup alpine tar czf /backup/gvm-db-backup-$(<span class="hljs-built_in">date</span> +%Y%m%d).tar.gz /data<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h2 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h2><ul><li><a href="https://greenbone.github.io/docs/latest/">Greenbone Community Documentation</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/greenbone/gvmd">Greenbone Community Containers</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/greenbone/gvmd/blob/main/docker-compose.yml">Docker Compose 示例</a></li></ul><hr><p><em>文档创建时间: 2026-03-03</em><br><em>最后更新: 2026-03-04</em></p>]]></content>
    
    
